<plot>Mosquito In The Room follows the struggles and process of six determined, hopeful kids as they make their own short film examining the monumental challenges their generation is set to inherit. Aged five to twelve, these kids ask tough questions about global warming, failing leadership, war and outmoded educational approaches with a view to discover whether its too late to reverse humanity's reckless, self-destructive path. If you think you're too small to make a difference, try sleeping with a Mosquito In The Room.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?378007</url></doc>
